This is my personal nvim configuration git-repo.

To prepare for a fresh setup, the following paths need to be moved:
~/.config/nvim
~/.local/share/nvim
~/.local/state/nvim

Or, if you need multiple setups, run nvim with NVIM_APPNAME.
For example, running:
$ NVIM_APPNAME=nvim_testcfg nvim
uses paths:
~/.config/nvim_testcfg
~/.local/share/nvim_testcfg
~/.local/state/nvim_testcfg

